---
title: Chipotle-Spiced Tilapia Tacos with Kiwi Pico de Gallo and Chipotle Crema
description: These are some feisty fish tacos because of the layer of chipotle spice that coats them. They’re snappy and crisp, too, thanks to a light dusting of cornstarch and a fry in the pan. But they also keep their cool with a kiwi tomato salsa and zesty sour cream. Which adds up to a recipe that’s amazing any night of the week. Sounds like a win-win!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c3cace1c445fa1ecf6cd632-b3edb409.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/chipotle-spiced-tilapia-tacos-5c3cace1c445fa1ecf6cd632-ff8ff8cb.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/chipotle-spiced-tilapia-tacos-5c3cace1c445fa1ecf6cd632
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
